-- Saudi Arabian Embassy Employee Shot Dead in Bangladesh, SPA Says
-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 2012-03-06T13:20:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-06/saudi-arabian-embassy-employee-shot-dead-in-bangladesh-spa-says.html
A Saudi Arabian employee at the
kingdom’s embassy to  Bangladesh  was shot dead in Dhaka last
night, the  Saudi Press Agency  reported, citing an unidentified
official at the  Ministry of Foreign Affairs .  Bangladesh authorities have begun an investigation into the
killing of Khalaf Al Ali while he was walking near his house,
the Riyadh-based official news service said. Saudi authorities
asked their Bangladeshi counterparts to intensify security for
employees of the kingdom’s diplomatic missions, SPA said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
